00:32:12.240 --> 00:32:13.350
I'm Kurt Raaflaub.

00:32:13.350 --> 00:32:14.610
I'm the editor of this work.

00:32:14.610 --> 00:32:16.830
But I want to start--

00:32:16.830 --> 00:32:20.760
I will build on
