00:32:28.800 --> 00:32:31.710
rare and high-quality teamwork.

00:32:31.710 --> 00:32:37.710
Bob has assembled a group
of very devoted specialists.

00:32:37.710 --> 00:32:41.820
And he, himself, has shown
throughout the process

00:32:41.820 --> 00:32:45.960
an incredible commitment
to producing this volume.

00:32:45.960 --> 00:32:50.250
I spent lots of time on it, but
he's spent nearly as much time

00:32:50.250 --> 00:32:51.360
on it.

00:32:51.360 --> 00:32:55.800
Spending hours and hours
talking with the cartographers,

00:32:55.800 --> 00:32:58.140
designing the maps himself.

00:32:58.140 --> 00:33:01.280
I corrected them, sent them
